source: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_SEQ_00<tab>Not all knights are indifferent to the plight of the commonfolk, and Ser Yaelle, one such earthbound warrior, wants a word with you.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_SEQ_00<tab>Yaelle a un travail qui pourrait vous faire gagner de l'argent facilement.

source: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_SEQ_01<tab>Ser Yaelle, she of the cool and speculative gaze, appears to enjoy the trust of the commonfolk; at their behest, she bids you slay a muttonmaw ogre. The bait is her very own karakul, Sebastian. But first, he must be captured with a length of brambleweed rope.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_SEQ_01<tab>Yaelle veut que vous chassiez <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 02F202AA0202 /var> qui dévore ré<var 16 /var>gu<var 16 /var>liè<var 16 /var>re<var 16 /var>ment du bétail près du camp. Commencez par utiliser <var 33 ((EventItem)) 03F61E87400202 /var> pour capturer <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E87410202 /var>, le karakul qui servira d'appât.

source: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_SEQ_02<tab>Take the bound karakul to Providence Point and leave him at the decoy point.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_SEQ_02<tab>Rendez-vous maintenant à Providence, au nord du camp de la Tête du dragon, et placez <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E87410202 /var> près de <var 33 ((EObj)) 03F61E8CCD0202 /var>.

source: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_SEQ_03<tab>With the bait set, all that remains is for the trap to be sprung. Hide yourself away and wait for the unwitting prey. Be ready to strike as soon as the ogre appears, or Sebastian will pay the price.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_SEQ_03<tab>Vous avez placé <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E87410202 /var> près de <var 33 ((EObj)) 03F61E8CCD0202 /var>. Tenez-vous prêt<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> et tuez <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 03F202AA0202 /var> qui se montrera.

source: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_SEQ_04<tab>The ogre is dead, and the poor karakul is safe, though trembling and wide-eyed. Unbind him that he may return to his mistress.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_SEQ_04<tab>Vous avez pu abattre <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 03F202AA0202 /var>. Libérez maintenant <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E87410202 /var>.

source: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_SEQ_05<tab>You have unbound the bound Sebastian, and he seems grateful to be free...and alive. Make your way back to Camp Dragonhead to speak with Ser Yaelle.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_SEQ_05<tab>Vous avez libéré Sebastian. Allez faire votre rapport à Yaelle.

source: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_SEQ_06<tab>Unlikely though it may seem, Sebastian has beaten you back to Ser Yaelle, as she informs you that she just finished brushing the brave karakul. The ogre will devour no more of the commonfolk's flock, and Ser Yaelle is well pleased.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_SEQ_06<tab>Grâce à vous, <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 03F202AA0202 /var> ne posera plus de problèmes au camp de la Tête du dragon. Yaelle était vraiment ravie de votre travail et pense faire appel à vos services de nouveau.

source: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_TODO_01<tab>Tether Sebastian to the decoy spot.
TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_TODO_02<tab>Lurk out of sight and slay the muttonmaw ogre.

TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_YAELLE_000_000<tab>Adventurer, I hear you like a good hunt! The commonfolk tell me they have lost a good many of their animals to an ogre. Their petitions have come to naught and so they come to me, and I in turn come to you.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_YAELLE_000_000<tab>Ça vous dirait de vous faire de l'argent facile<var 1D /var>? Pour ça, il vous suffira de partir à la chasse à l'<var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF202AA0202 /var>.

source: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_YAELLE_000_001<tab>We must needs have a decoy for this hunt, but I would not ask the folk to risk more of their livelihood. Let us use my own beloved Sebastian to lure this ogre out into the open.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_YAELLE_000_001<tab>Notre <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF202AA0202 /var> est un monstre intelligent qui ne se montre pas facilement, mais en utilisant mon Sebastian comme appât, vous devriez réussir à le faire sortir de sa cachette.

source: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_YAELLE_000_002<tab>Oh, he is my darling karakul─a wise knight keeps her own source of wool. Yes, Sebastian has clothed me since I came to this camp and will someday feed me, too, no doubt. But today, you will return him to me safe and sound.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_YAELLE_000_002<tab>Ah oui, Sebastian est le nom de mon karakul de compagnie. Vous allez devoir vous servir de <var 33 ((EventItem)) 07F61E87400202 /var> pour le capturer. Ça ne devrait pas être trop difficile pour quelqu'un comme vous. Bonne chance<var 1D /var>!
TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_DUMMY_000_010<tab>ドラゴンヘッド周辺の「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2031B01 /var>」(enpc)に「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E874001 /var>」を使って羊をゲット。
TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_DUMMY_000_020<tab>「<var 28 ((EventItem)) F61E874101 /var>」を指定地点に置いて、「<var 28 ((EObj)) F61E8E8B01 /var>」で待機。

source: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_SYSTEM_000_025<tab>You loose Sebastian from his bonds. Leave him be and he will make his own way back.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_SYSTEM_000_025<tab>Vous avez libéré Sebastian. Laissez-le aller, il devrait retrouver son chemin tout seul.

source: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_YAELLE_000_030<tab>Ah, there you are, and let us toast to a job well done! I've just finished brushing Sebastian. He will get some squash with his hay tonight.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_YAELLE_000_030<tab>Ah, vous revoilà<var 1D /var>! Vous savez, <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 07F202AA0202 /var> venait ré<var 16 /var>gu<var 16 /var>liè<var 16 /var>re<var 16 /var>ment près du camp dévorer quelques-unes des bêtes que nous laissons en pâture. Je suis sûre que Sebastian est ravi d'avoir pu rendre service à ses pairs.

source: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_YAELLE_000_031<tab>Corentiaux spoke highly of you and he is right, I think. There is much to be said of a <var 08 E905 ((woman)) ((man)) /var> who is sworn not to a master but to <var 08 E905 ((her)) ((his)) /var> work. With adventurers, one need only speak the end and they devise their own means.
target: TEXT_GAIUSB706_00901_YAELLE_000_031<tab>J'ai bien fait de m'adresser à vous<var 1D /var>! Je vous remets cette récompense avec plaisir. Vous pouvez être sûr<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> que je ne manquerai pas de vous demander votre aide à nouveau<var 1D /var>!
